text: Annovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Leninsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Yermolayevo, 7 km from Bugulchan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Annovka, Kuyurgazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
